{
  "id": "69a9343c18d9ae6912d97cfe",
  "title": "ローマ字入力の効率化の案",
  "created": 1772696637,
  "updated": 1772744512,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a9343c18d9ae6912d97cfe",
      "text": "ローマ字入力の効率化の案",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772697268
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af154",
      "text": "cf. [速記タイピング]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772696637
    },
    {
      "id": "69a938ac0000000000ae5384",
      "text": "#ローマ字入力",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772697773,
      "updated": 1772729511
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af155",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772696637
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af156",
      "text": "子音字の連続をあ段とみなす",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772696637
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af157",
      "text": "\t`wtsh`→ `わたしは`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772696637
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af158",
      "text": " `x` → `っ`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772696637
    },
    {
      "id": "69a936bc000000000024a6b3",
      "text": "\t`l` → `ん`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772697277,
      "updated": 1772697294
    },
    {
      "id": "69a976990000000000ea22b7",
      "text": "\tア段とみなさずに類推するのはどうだろう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772713626,
      "updated": 1772713643
    },
    {
      "id": "69a976ab0000000000ea22b8",
      "text": "\t\t漢字入力でも類推しているんだから、今更難しい話でもなかろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772713643,
      "updated": 1772713729
    },
    {
      "id": "69a977430000000000ea22b9",
      "text": "\t\t`krm` → `カルマ` / `くるま` (車) / `きりみ` (切り身)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772713795,
      "updated": 1772713872
    },
    {
      "id": "69a977930000000000ea22ba",
      "text": "\t\t結構面倒くさいな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772713875,
      "updated": 1772713881
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9779e0000000000ea22bb",
      "text": "\t\t\tでもこれって漢字を一発変換できる人から見た時の日本語の変換の面倒くささと同じようなものか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772713887,
      "updated": 1772713923
    },
    {
      "id": "69a978230000000000ea22bc",
      "text": "\t\t\tsee: [漢字直接入力]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772714020,
      "updated": 1772714097
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9786b0000000000ea22c0",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/漢字直接入力 漢字直接入力]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772714092,
      "updated": 1772714092
    },
    {
      "id": "69a978310000000000ea22be",
      "text": " \t\t\t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/無連想式漢字直接入力 無連想式漢字直接入力]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772714033,
      "updated": 1772714054
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b2f50000000000edf7fa",
      "text": " \t\t\tこれは関係ない感想だけど、無連想式漢字直接入力はもはやエスパーじみている…[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772729078,
      "updated": 1772729156
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af159",
      "text": "\t\tそうか、辞書セットを用意すればいいのか。かなり複雑化しそうだけど、今なら機械学習モデルが予測してくれるか[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772729462
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b4130000000000edf7fd",
      "text": "\t\tちなみに、自分は既存のIMEのローマ字テーブルを変更する程度で手っ取り早く手にできることを重視していた[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772729364,
      "updated": 1772729498
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9b3460000000000edf7fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772729159,
      "updated": 1772729159
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af15a",
      "text": "未使用文字",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772696637
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af15b",
      "text": "\tC",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772696637
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af15d",
      "text": "\tQ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772696637
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9343c00000000000af15e",
      "text": "\tX",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772696637,
      "updated": 1772696637
    },
    {
      "id": "69a938aa0000000000ae5379",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772697771,
      "updated": 1772697771
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef120000000000c2c0c1",
      "text": "エイリアスをつくる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772744467,
      "updated": 1772744470
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef150000000000c2c0c3",
      "text": "\t`ls` → `リスト`みたいな",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772744470,
      "updated": 1772744485
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef250000000000c2c0c4",
      "text": "\t\t本質的には辞書登録と同じ？",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772744486,
      "updated": 1772744495
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef370000000000c2c0c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772744504,
      "updated": 1772744504
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef380000000000c2c0c7",
      "text": "エイリアス + 同時押し的なやつ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772744505,
      "updated": 1772744509
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef2e0000000000c2c0c5",
      "text": "\t[ステノワード]的というか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772744495,
      "updated": 1772744512
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef3f0000000000c2c0c8",
      "text": "\t\t",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772744512,
      "updated": 1772744512
    },
    {
      "id": "69a9ef130000000000c2c0c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772744467,
      "updated": 1772744467
    }
  ]
}